1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:24,289 --> 00:01:28,980
[In the Name of the Brother]

3
00:01:29,289 --> 00:01:31,830
[Episode 25]

4
00:01:56,630 --> 00:01:57,550
Mr. Li.

5
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,470
Mr. Li!

6
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,490
Something bothering you?

7
00:02:09,509 --> 00:02:10,710
Not really.

8
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,180
Just a bit disappointed.

9
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:15,180
I came all the way here

10
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,930
just to return in vain.

11
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:22,860
Mr. Li.

12
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:27,500
Who exactly are you?

13
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:38,110
With all due respect,

14
00:02:38,450 --> 00:02:41,400
you don't know how to write the cursive script.

15
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,120
No.

16
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,280
You can't write calligraphy at all,

17
00:02:46,829 --> 00:02:47,630
right?

18
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,690
You guessed right.

19
00:02:52,380 --> 00:02:55,790
I'm Intelligence Unit Chief, Song Zhuowen.

20
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,090
Mr. Li Cunliang

21
00:02:57,090 --> 00:02:59,290
was injured in an assassination in Harbin,

22
00:02:59,290 --> 00:03:00,720
so I had to come instead.

23
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,470
I still have a question.

24
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:05,230
Go ahead.

25
00:03:05,730 --> 00:03:08,490
I'm sorry for staining your shirt.

26
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:11,010
But when I told the orderly

27
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,450
to wash it immediately,

28
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,790
do you recall how you reacted?

29
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:21,350
Stop it!

30
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,310
I'll do it myself.

31
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:42,079
Didn't you notice your invisible ink's missing?

32
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:44,740
I have it.

33
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,810
Save the explanations.

34
00:03:52,810 --> 00:03:54,420
When we return to Harbin,

35
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:56,829
Mr. Asano will tell us what this is.

36
00:04:10,050 --> 00:04:11,590
Don't move! Let him go!

37
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:54,000
Don't move!

38
00:05:24,670 --> 00:05:25,500
Turn around!

39
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,140
Turn around!

40
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,400
Fly to Harbin!

41
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:30,990
Turn around!

42
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,040
Tell me who you are!

43
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,870
Turn around!

44
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,520
I'm still worth using.

45
00:05:42,090 --> 00:05:43,530
We are all worthless.

46
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,420
No one can go back.

47
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,960
Song Zhuowen's death

48
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:18,910
means nothing to me!

49
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:21,020
It's your business to mourn him!

50
00:06:21,030 --> 00:06:22,550
Go back to your office

51
00:06:22,550 --> 00:06:23,230
or home!

52
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,270
Go cry and drink

53
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:26,200
and burn your Manchurian incense!

54
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,960
He's an outstanding person.

55
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,390
You said it yourself!

56
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:31,020
An outstanding person

57
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,440
should die for his faith.

58
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,460
That's the spirit of a warrior!

59
00:06:36,810 --> 00:06:38,909
From the day he chose this job,

60
00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:40,110
he'd already known

61
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,990
he could die anytime.

62
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:45,040
Song Zhuowen has faith.

63
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:49,220
Although he failed his mission

64
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:51,120
and didn't catch the mole!

65
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:56,500
Have you considered...

66
00:06:58,090 --> 00:07:00,540
who should take up his position?

67
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,580
Is it so urgent?

68
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:02,650
Of course!

69
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:09,330
The Secret Service can't go a day

70
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,860
without the Intelligence Unit Chief.

71
00:07:18,490 --> 00:07:20,330
I'll make arrangements now.

72
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:46,170
Sorry to disturb you.

73
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:03,880
Write a report to the Army Headquarters.

74
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,980
Dongning Fortress is no longer safe.

75
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:09,790
Cut off all its connections with the outside world

76
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,690
as soon as possible.

77
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:16,480
Like a lizard cutting off its tail.

78
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:20,290
I have another opinion.

79
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:21,600
What?

80
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,360
The plane accident

81
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:25,340
was not due to bad weather

82
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:27,470
or a mechanical malfunction.

83
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:29,860
Since the higher-ups think so,

84
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:33,380
let's not create more trouble.

85
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,179
Humans...

86
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:42,450
really can't defy fate.

87
00:08:42,659 --> 00:08:43,960
Who would've thought

88
00:08:43,970 --> 00:08:46,200
the heavens would take Song Zhuowen away?

89
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,930
It saved us a lot of trouble.

90
00:08:49,370 --> 00:08:49,930
Here.

91
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,520
Put this on.

92
00:08:51,690 --> 00:08:52,790
Put this on.

93
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,280
This feels like a special occasion.

94
00:08:56,610 --> 00:08:57,610
So, buddy,

95
00:08:57,780 --> 00:09:00,130
isn't it time you come back to work?

96
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:03,590
Only if Guan Xue comes to beg me sincerely.

97
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:09,130
Has she visited you once in the hospital?

98
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,370
No.

99
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:20,070
So I need either her or Mr. Asano

100
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,910
to come and beg me.

101
00:09:22,930 --> 00:09:24,650
Don't be ridiculous.

102
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,240
Quit while you're ahead.

103
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:36,180
But I've not witnessed his death

104
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,730
myself.

105
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:42,420
Nobody has seen

106
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:45,750
Zhuowen's corpse with their own eyes.

107
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,980
What if he rises from the ashes?

108
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,110
Take that back!

109
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:52,250
Take that back!

110
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:53,610
Keep calm.

111
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,180
Wait a little more.

112
00:09:58,210 --> 00:09:58,700
Here.

113
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,950
The latest news I got at noon

114
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:19,190
said the plane

115
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,380
crashed.

116
00:10:21,940 --> 00:10:23,860
A Japanese search and rescue team

117
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:24,600
found it.

118
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:32,750
Because you're his brother

119
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,010
and his only family,

120
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,780
if there's anything you need,

121
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,760
we'll try our best to satisfy them.

122
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:46,180
Don't resent the organization.

123
00:10:46,490 --> 00:10:47,940
Because back then...

124
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:51,620
When the organization

125
00:10:51,660 --> 00:10:54,040
sent Zhuowen for this mission,

126
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:56,360
no one expected such a thing to happen.

127
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:59,450
I'm devastated by Zhuowen's sacrifice too!

128
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:02,790
There are also kids

129
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:03,910
younger than Zhuowen.

130
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:04,500
All of them, I...

131
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:05,950
I watched them grow up.

132
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:06,990
I watched them fall

133
00:11:06,990 --> 00:11:07,870
and grow up.

134
00:11:09,010 --> 00:11:10,750
And then they died one by one

135
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,420
in front of me.

136
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,990
Whenever I spend

137
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:20,630
even just

138
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:21,420
a few months

139
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:24,860
with some young kid,

140
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:26,510
it's as if I've known them

141
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,670
for a lifetime.

142
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,370
Enough, Qian.

143
00:11:36,410 --> 00:11:38,140
You can't do anything.

144
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:44,800
I did do nothing.

145
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:47,580
Back then, I was the dumbest in our team.

146
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,380
Before Secretary Luo was arrested,

147
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,780
he put me in charge.

148
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,120
Many comrades questioned it.

149
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:57,140
How can he be in charge?

150
00:11:58,460 --> 00:12:00,000
He says he can do anything

151
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,580
but fails at everything.

152
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:03,730
Who'd wanna entrust their life to him?

153
00:12:04,210 --> 00:12:05,970
They all said that about me.

154
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,990
But I think they're right.

155
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:12,990
Later, Luo said this to them,

156
00:12:12,990 --> 00:12:13,940
that as a member

157
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:15,400
of an underground party,

158
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:17,810
it's not about how strong you are,

159
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:20,030
but how long you can live.

160
00:12:20,570 --> 00:12:22,070
How can one live long?

161
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,120
By abiding by the rules.

162
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:26,130
I disagree.

163
00:12:28,170 --> 00:12:29,060
I think about

164
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:32,990
how to let the enemy die before us.

165
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:38,890
Yes.

166
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,150
Zhuowu, you don't know this,

167
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:52,830
but...

168
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:56,120
there are about a dozen of us old folks from Manchukuo

169
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:59,090
who are all considered as capable.

170
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:00,600
But they all died.

171
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,840
I'm the only one left.

172
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:09,310
So, I brought young people in.

173
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:10,890
One batch

174
00:13:12,490 --> 00:13:13,650
after another...

175
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,040
Now it's Zhuowen.

176
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:23,220
In the end, all of them died.

177
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:25,060
I'm the only one left again.

178
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:26,300
Do you know

179
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,580
how that feels?

180
00:13:30,790 --> 00:13:32,880
This life is worse than death.

181
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:36,570
But I have to persist.

182
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,340
I have to.

183
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:44,100
Enough.

184
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:45,430
Persist?

185
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:50,480
No wonder you live longer than them.

186
00:13:57,960 --> 00:14:00,040
Qian, don't worry.

187
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:02,530
My brother won't die easily.

188
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:06,060
When we were young, the fortune teller said he was tough.

189
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:08,010
He can't be dead.

190
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:33,530
This is my oath.

191
00:14:34,290 --> 00:14:34,900
First,

192
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,420
fight for communism for life.

193
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,310
Second,

194
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,990
put the Party's interests above all else.

195
00:14:42,970 --> 00:14:43,570
Third,

196
00:14:43,850 --> 00:14:45,480
abide by the Party's rules.

197
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:47,480
Four,

198
00:14:47,690 --> 00:14:50,750
never fear difficulties and always work for the Party.

199
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:52,260
Five,

200
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:54,530
be a role model to everyone.

201
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:55,790
Six,

202
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,580
keep the Party's secrets.

203
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,590
Seven,

204
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:01,300
have faith in the Party.

205
00:15:02,230 --> 00:15:02,840
Eight,

206
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:04,530
be undaunted

207
00:15:04,660 --> 00:15:06,390
and forever loyal to the Party.

208
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:08,240
Yours sincerely,

209
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:09,840
Song Zhuowu.

210
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,330
Stop crying.

211
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:53,020
Hold it in.

212
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:54,570
He was just a tool.

213
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:56,550
Why are you crying?

214
00:16:56,570 --> 00:16:57,710
If it weren't for Wen,

215
00:16:57,710 --> 00:16:58,790
we would've died twice!

216
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,160
Fates are predestined!

217
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:02,330
It only proves I shouldn't die.

218
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:02,990
Xue!

219
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,700
Stop being so inhumane!

220
00:17:17,349 --> 00:17:17,950
Sit down.

221
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:19,490
Let's eat.

222
00:17:21,099 --> 00:17:22,200
Sit down and eat!

223
00:18:21,540 --> 00:18:22,340
Kai.

224
00:18:22,970 --> 00:18:23,910
Life's short.

225
00:18:23,910 --> 00:18:25,310
Don't be swayed by emotions,

226
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,470
or you'll be controlled...

227
00:18:26,470 --> 00:18:27,640
-Enough!
-You...

228
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:31,690
I, Guan Kai,

229
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:34,030
your brother,

230
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:35,190
am a stumbling block

231
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,840
who hinders your future!

232
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:17,780
Who is it?

233
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:20,610
Me!

234
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,720
Why are you here at this hour?

235
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,850
Something urgent!

236
00:19:48,890 --> 00:19:51,160
The munitions warehouse was burgled?

237
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:54,030
We lost a lot of explosives.

238
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:56,710
It's enough to blow up the Police building.

239
00:20:14,010 --> 00:20:16,380
Let Public Security take care of it.

240
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:19,000
Let's handle Zhuowen's funeral first.

241
00:20:21,210 --> 00:20:23,140
This is your urgent matter?

242
00:20:24,530 --> 00:20:25,800
You're right.

243
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:29,030
This is my urgent matter.

244
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:31,660
You...

245
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:32,260
Hu Bin!

246
00:20:34,490 --> 00:20:35,050
Hu Bin!

247
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,160
Hu Bin!

248
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:37,950
Hu Bin!

249
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:42,930
Don't move.

250
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:45,370
Don't move.

251
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:08,180
Why don't you point the gun at me?

252
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:11,000
It's fine if you insist.

253
00:21:10,890 --> 00:21:13,290
Now you know I'm not to be messed with.

254
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:16,680
Touch me after I die.

255
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:20,410
If you kill me now,

256
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:22,060
you'll be in big trouble.

257
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:26,110
Song Zhuowen's dead.

258
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:27,510
Dead, you know?

259
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,660
It'll still never be your turn.

260
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:42,830
Hu Bin.

261
00:21:44,250 --> 00:21:47,100
People hold grudges and forget acts of kindness.

262
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:49,760
I've been hard on you all these years.

263
00:21:50,060 --> 00:21:52,230
I knew you'd do this someday.

264
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,320
I'm not a fool.

265
00:21:56,120 --> 00:21:56,920
You're not.

266
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:58,980
I'm the fool.

267
00:22:22,190 --> 00:22:24,100
How many times have I told you?

268
00:22:24,830 --> 00:22:26,730
There's no shortcut here.

269
00:22:27,690 --> 00:22:29,310
If you can't fly to the sky,

270
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:31,160
just crawl earnestly.

271
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:37,350
Don't worry about my situation.

272
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:42,250
Let's pretend this never happened.

273
00:22:44,610 --> 00:22:47,450
You have until dawn to move on,

274
00:22:48,220 --> 00:22:50,060
or I'll cut ties with you.

275
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,840
Prepare for Zhuowen's funeral.

276
00:23:10,490 --> 00:23:11,150
Go.

277
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:23,500
You'll not realize your folly until the worst has happened.

278
00:24:21,320 --> 00:24:22,860
I saw Hu Bin at the door.

279
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:46,690
Our organization in Fengtian

280
00:25:46,690 --> 00:25:49,280
was severely destroyed by the Japanese and Manchukuo Secret Services.

281
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:50,560
Many comrades were arrested.

282
00:25:50,560 --> 00:25:52,290
That line's concealed for now.

283
00:25:52,630 --> 00:25:53,590
So we...

284
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:04,730
What do you mean by this?

285
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:06,610
Qian, leave me alone.

286
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:08,960
I can't be bothered about rules now.

287
00:26:10,780 --> 00:26:11,660
As you said,

288
00:26:12,390 --> 00:26:15,430
I've worked with you for only a few months,

289
00:26:15,430 --> 00:26:16,430
not even a year.

290
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:18,980
I have to avenge Zhuowen no matter what.

291
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:20,500
Or it might be too late.

292
00:26:24,100 --> 00:26:26,610
Are you the only one who wants revenge?

293
