00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:11,190
Be extra careful.

329
00:31:12,340 --> 00:31:13,510
Once you get in contact

330
00:31:13,510 --> 00:31:15,150
with comrades in Harbin,

331
00:31:15,150 --> 00:31:17,340
get them to build a new transport line.

332
00:31:17,340 --> 00:31:18,050
Xia.

333
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:21,100
Rest assured.

334
00:31:22,170 --> 00:31:24,480
