338
00:31:34,740 --> 00:31:35,550
Remember,

339
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:38,510
at 3 p.m. on the 12th of next month,

340
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:41,190
I'll wait for him at the teahouse on the west of Minfu Street

341
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:41,840
in Harbin.

342
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:50,510
I got it.

343
00:31:51,930 --> 00:31:53,780
Three p.m. on the 12th of next month.

344
00:31:53,780 --> 00:31:56,380
Teahouse on the west of Minfu Street in Harbin.

345
